## How to Use

1. **Open** [index.html](file:///Users/gokalp/Library/Mobile%20Documents/com~apple~CloudDocs/Projects/TimeLineDiagram/index.html) in your browser
2. **Add lanes** using the "+ Add" button in the sidebar
3. **Create boxes** by clicking and dragging on a lane track
4. **Edit boxes** by clicking on them to open the properties panel
5. **Zoom** using the +/‚àí buttons or "Fit" to auto-scale
6. **Export** using Save (JSON), PNG, or SVG buttons
